Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.86,0:00:02.60,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}ただひとり
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.92,0:00:08.79,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}迷い込む旅の中で
